Subject: Firewalls with pfSense
Description: Learn how to set up and configure pfSense, the open source network firewall distribution based on the FreeBSD operating system. I will be covering loading pfSense, configuring interfaces, setting up a VPN that will work windows & linux, and explaining how to setup and use some of the popular plugins  Speakers include:Tom Lawrence - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
